{"tid":1713521,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日新界南（荃灣手足入尼）","createTime":"2019-11-12T17:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T00:47:01.000Z","uid":280214,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca14f931e24f7dadc4e49511c6a3abb534d0808","tid":1713521,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:53:45.000Z","msg":"首先，我地聽日既目的分散警力，暴大屬於新界南，姐係荃，葵，青，火炭，大埔，沙田etc 。<br />\n<br />\n而荃灣個位係好撚尷尷尬有三間狗屋包撚住（大窩口果間） （愉景果間）（青衣果間）代表咩？危險？唔係。姐係最有效分散警力一個。唔該人地暴大比班狗打撚到上心口我喊左咁撚多轉。我知道荃灣手足係弱勢DD，可能沒沙田咁強勢。但唔緊要，慢慢學。<br />\n<br />\n首先，聽日一係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陣地</span></span>一係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">快閃</span></span>，遮係一定要唔該<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要見到傘陣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其次，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見到狗同Tg唔撚好走[要同佢地死過，我地勝在多人一人一舊磚都打到佢地On99/red]</span>要記住，我地既目的係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]分散警力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n再者，我地唔可以係一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被動</span>[/既角色size=5]，唔好諗[size=5]裝修</span>，喇，我地目的係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">引狗</span></span>，邊到最撚多狗？<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗屋</span></span>囉。要裝唔該<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">狗屋優先</span></span>。咁樣先可以引班狗出尼，而唔係係到條條Fing咁樣（前題要set曬RB先）<br />\n<br />\n最後，果句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護自己</span></span>唔該聽日係要同班狗死過。我相信荃灣手足唔係流既。<br />\n<br />\n大家聽日見，我己經預左中槍既風險。唔該求下你地罷工，出尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該。我真係好撚想救暴大。求下你地。"},{"pid":"55d2bf964c54ebeeacd99ed7c77cfb50952164bc","tid":1713521,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ff2a6857dfabba7e87a3454f7f85aeb9ed776e05","tid":1713521,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"